# V16 teaches: Scoring with world.awardScore() and victory daemon

# Check initial score
> score
[OK: contains "scored 0"]

# Collect zoo map (5 pts) and brochure
> take map
[OK: contains "Taken"]

> take brochure
[OK: contains "Taken"]

# Read brochure (5 pts)
> read brochure
[OK: contains "WILLOWBROOK"]

